rows.label: qst300205_msg0001
rows.name: Sorry about all this. I know it's a pain.

rows.label: qst300205_msg0002
rows.name:
But it's time we set things straight.
Show 'em the younger generation's still
got every right to be calling the shots.

rows.label: qst300205_msg0101
rows.name:
You beat Vorden and Jugger?!
That's some bragging rights!

rows.label: qst300205_msg0201
rows.name: What a battle. I have no regrets!

rows.label: qst300205_msg0202
rows.name:
If Vandham were here today,
he'd be so proud of you!
